Prediction

Matrice de confusion

CONDITION_POSITIVE CONDITION_NEGATIVE
PREDICT_POSITIVE (P) True Positive (TP) False Positive (FP)
PREDICT_NEGATIVE (N) False Negative (FN) False Negative (TN)

Formule mathmatiques (1)

Taux derreur (accuracy) : ACC = \(\frac{TP+TN} {TP+TN+FP+TF}\)

Sensibilit (sensibility) : TPR = \(\frac{TP} {TP+FN}\)

Specificit (specificity) : TNR = \(\frac{TN} {TN+FP}\)

Formule mathmatiques (2)

F1 score : F1 = \(\frac{2*TP} {2*TP+FP+FN}\)

Coefficient de corrlation de Matthews : MCC =

\(\frac{TP*TN-FP*FN} {((TP+FP)(TP+FN)(TN+FP)(TN+FN))^{-1}}\)
